{"tid":1814331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後見到裝修、獅鳥，煩請各位和理非大叫「支持手足」並拍掌鼓勵","createTime":"2020-01-07T01:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T02:30:59.000Z","uid":88167,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"078e071bdf542153c0c62e9b2e1f1a9fd8380fb9","tid":1814331,"uid":88167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:09:41.000Z","msg":"支持勇武先係和理非應該做嘅事，咁先係真正「和勇不分」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要你肯拍個靚手，嗌下支持、加油，乜撚野鬼都係你手足<br />\n真亦假時假亦真，假亦真時真亦假，真真假假，有乜撚野所謂?<br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話加多句「香港獨立，唯一出路」、「國難當前，和勇不分」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做唔到既就返屋企打飛機等滅族算啦，無貢獻都唔緊要，捉鬼累死手足落地獄死一萬次都唔撚夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c813343589415f7cc22f12c2873ad5a761c37396","tid":1814331,"uid":321749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我系五毛：我就快贏了^_^<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1814310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1814310</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8fb7e3f3cb48e9ac2ed6c3110f39a6b0c413bd83","tid":1814331,"uid":249563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:10:25.000Z","msg":"They: 多謝黑警"},{"pid":"a7f88092f48bd1c3edcffb58833b4c6392e42394","tid":1814331,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fb7e3f3cb48e9ac2ed6c3110f39a6b0c413bd83","tid":1814331,"uid":249563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:10:25.000Z","msg":"They: 多謝黑警"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:12:25.000Z","msg":"所以要宣傳見到呢類post要多謝手足，多謝勇武"},{"pid":"7e6016c276edaae58b4e6d1d9cf74666a6ce9f13","tid":1814331,"uid":88167,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8fb7e3f3cb48e9ac2ed6c3110f39a6b0c413bd83","tid":1814331,"uid":249563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:10:25.0